{"tid":888580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日AV片商推10周年紀念商品　三上悠亞等身罩杯滑鼠墊價格破萬","createTime":"2018-11-04T00:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T06:32:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"486bfa3fb6b7ac755c1891f6761758bff29b585e","tid":888580,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"在台灣擁有高人氣的日本AV界小天后三上悠亞，以及25歲G罩杯AV女優高橋聖子，據傳日本片商MUTEKI推出的10週年紀念特別商品，將為2人打造等身大罩杯滑鼠墊，消息一出馬上讓不少粉絲相當期待。<br />\n專營情趣用品代購及「試用」、有情趣用品女王之稱的SallyQ於批踢踢japanavgirls版發文透露，有業務與她接洽，這款身大罩杯滑鼠墊採用仿真胸部觸感的高品質矽膠，預計今年底可接單生產，大約明年2至3月出貨，將由日本國內工廠生產，強調極仿真手感。<br />\n但因為是接單生產，欲下訂者無法取消訂單外，售價加上運費和關稅，台灣預計販售價將超過萬元，也考驗粉絲的消費能力，不少網友看了也紛紛留言「好想要啊！可是超貴」、「我覺得出等身造型枕頭應該會比滑鼠墊實用」、「真的有人敢把放在桌上嗎XDD」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181104/640_ad5e3f40cfd56797ca655b7d017127d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181104%2F640_ad5e3f40cfd56797ca655b7d017127d2.jpg&h=32d1274f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181104/640_b26af56746503616c01cb2e8e30b0752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181104%2F640_b26af56746503616c01cb2e8e30b0752.jpg&h=eb6380a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5636dd2290915588f3c20558846e4a09c80055db","tid":888580,"uid":8477,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"用黎劣尻一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fac52707ba60a7b8f3999ebc61d786b561f405","tid":888580,"uid":90791,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"滑鼠墊打飛機超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede3f2b25139830080358e0a52a5f070e3d807ae","tid":888580,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":1,"scor